Subject: [PATCH 1583/2241] fix: net: mvpp2x: fix RSS for IPv6 packets with
 different DA

Issue:
Wrong classifier field ID for IPv6 DA were set and RSS doesn't
worked for IPv6 packets with different DA.

Change-Id: Ic27a87f12cda412caff78fa8a9820c9cffa42e35
Signed-off-by: Stefan Chulski <stefanc@marvell.com>
Reviewed-on: http://vgitil04.il.marvell.com:8080/38962
Reviewed-by: Ehud Naim <ehudn@marvell.com>
Reviewed-by: Yuval Caduri <cyuval@marvell.com>
Tested-by: iSoC Platform CI <ykjenk@marvell.com>
Reviewed-by: Omri Itach <omrii@marvell.com>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/marvell/mvpp2x/mv_pp2x_hw_type.h | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/ethernet/marvell/mvpp2x/mv_pp2x_hw_type.h b/drivers/net/ethernet/marvell/mvpp2x/mv_pp2x_hw_type.h
index 1781d81..9e33d1d 100644
--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/marvell/mvpp2x/mv_pp2x_hw_type.h
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/marvell/mvpp2x/mv_pp2x_hw_type.h
@@ -1709,7 +1709,7 @@ enum mv_pp2x_cls_filed_id {
 	MVPP2_CLS_FIELD_IP4SA = 0x10,
 	MVPP2_CLS_FIELD_IP4DA = 0x11,
 	MVPP2_CLS_FIELD_IP6SA = 0x17,
-	MVPP2_CLS_FIELD_IP6DA = 0x18,
+	MVPP2_CLS_FIELD_IP6DA = 0x1A,
 	MVPP2_CLS_FIELD_L4SIP = 0x1D,
 	MVPP2_CLS_FIELD_L4DIP = 0x1E,
 };
